## Step 4: Deploy Web App

1. Click Deploy → New Deployment
2. Select:
   Web App
3. Set:
   • Execute as → Me
   • Who has access → Anyone
4. Click Deploy
5. Authorize permissions
6. Copy the generated Web App URL

---

## Step 5: Add URL in ESP32 Code

Replace:

```cpp
String serverName = "YOUR_WEB_APP_URL";
```

With:

```cpp
String serverName = "https://script.google.com/macros/s/xxxxxxxxxxxx/exec";
```

---

## Step 6: Upload ESP32 Code

1. Connect ESP32 to computer
2. Select correct COM port
3. Upload Arduino code

---

## Step 7: Test the System

1. Scan RFID card
2. LCD displays ENTRY or EXIT
3. Attendance data automatically appears in Google Sheets

